Articles.Content:
This is my new space program.

Prosper 1: First Satellite

![XEK5HE9.png](http://i.imgur.com/XEK5HE9.png)

Prosper 1 was the first satellite placed in low Kerbin orbit.

Prosper 2: First Solar Powered Satellite

![QjyPgXE.png](http://i.imgur.com/QjyPgXE.png)

Prosper 2 was the first satellite to be launched and also the first to use solar power.

There are my first missions. I will update when I can and also tell me what you think of these satellites.
Very cool but simple probes! Cant wait to see what you do next!

The mods I'm using are:

Dmagic orbital science 

Mechjeb

Clamshell fairings 

Tarsier space tech

And kerbal alarm clock

Dawn 1 marked the first Kerbal to go into orbit and return safetly

> [Javascript is disabled. View full album](//imgur.com/a/HHZTY)

About a year and a half after Dawn 1, KSC launched the Frontier 1 Eve Probe
